    More About AgTech Consultancy Services

    Our Story

     VISION STATEMENT                                    

    To embrace the challenges of advancing our people, their communities, their aspirations and their global integration by way of using ICT and AgScience technologies. Developing and harnessing our technological expertise to bridge the breadth of technological advancement and be parallel to the world leaders in ICT and agriculture industries.

     MISSION STATEMENT                                    

    A focused implementation of ICT and AgScience technology that is driven by the PNG market, delivering leading edge and innovative technologies that are economically viable. The depth of our local knowledge and our technological expertise are the corner stones of our business.
